<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT75">
<l>nākkoṇṭu māṉiṭam pāṭēṉ nalamākat</l>
<l>tīkkoṇṭa ceñcaṭaiyāṉ ceṉṟeṉṟum pūkkoṇṭu</l>
<l>vallavā ṟētta makiḻāta vaikuntac</l>
<l>celvaṉār cēvaṭimēṟ pāṭṭu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>‘I shall not sing of mankind with [my] tongue.</l>
<l>[My] songs [will] be on the red feet of the Lord of Vaikuṇṭha,</l>
<l>who did not [condescend] to be pleased, as [Śiva] with fire-like red matted locks,</l>
<l>went carrying flowers to always extol [Him] as much as [he] could,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that good occurred [to him].’</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
